<div class="app-container">
    <h1>Daily Plan - December 27, 2025</h1>
    <h2>AI Chat Search Features & Integration Testing</h2>

    <div class="last-updated">
        <strong>Date:</strong> Saturday, December 27, 2025 |
        <strong>Focus:</strong> Test AI Chat search capabilities and system integration |
        <strong>Status:</strong> 📋 Planning Phase - Dependent on Dec 26 Results
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <h3>⚠️ CONDITIONAL PLAN - Requires Dec 26 Success</h3>
        <p><strong>This plan executes ONLY IF December 26 testing passes (Phase 3-4).</strong></p>
